reviewText: I was disappointed to have been duped into ordering this item. Had I known it wouldn't work in any of the DVDs in the UNITED STATES I never would have ordered it. I want to return it, however there is no option to do so. :-/
It wouldnt work in my dvd, becaise it is formatted for Ireland!!!!!

Came rite on time and American dad is one of my favorite animated shows it was good as usual it never fails I've been trying to find new season to this series and I couldn't but Amazon is awesome I think I'm addicted to Amazon now this was my first internet buy and I'm amazed!!
